  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Cut the squid into 1-inch pieces.",
    "3. Thread the squid, onion, parsley, cilantro, and mint onto skewers.",
    "4. Brush the skewers with olive oil and season with salt and pepper.",
    "5. Grill the skewers for 5-7 minutes per side, or until the squid is cooked through.",
    "6. While the skewers are grilling, mix the harissa and lime juice in a small bowl.",
    "7. Brush the harissa-lime mixture onto the skewers during the last minute of grilling.",
    "8. Serve hot and garnish with additional parsley and mint, if desired."
  ],
